:: Gnoll Reckless Charge {"position":"1100,900","size":"100,100"}
Before your foe has time to pivot, you erupt into a furious charge! The stumbling beast freezes for a moment, before meeting your charge with open jaws. As you throw a punch, his jaws close around it, dusting the air with red. You let out a cry of pain, frantically writhing to get free, but it's no use. His incredible bite strength tears your forearm clean off, the white hot pain blinding you to the claws heading for your abdomen. 

You fall to the ground, mind racing for a way out, but [[finding nothing.|Death]]


