:: Present Day {"position":"900,700","size":"100,100"}
"Thanks for the tip, Barb! I'll have it dealt with before dawn hits your window!" Silas says, standing up from his seat at the diner.

"Oh, thank you! Glad we can always rely on our local monster hunter!"

As Silas walks out the door, his friendly smile hardens into cold concentration. "//Great, another monster just on the outskirts of town. That's the tenth monster sighting this week! Not to mention there being a damn gnoll in the forest! Gnolls live in savannas, how did it even get here?!//" Silas thinks to himself, making his way home. "//Whatever. Nothing I can't handle. I'll just grab my gear, get to the scene, dispatch it and be home for dinner!//"

